Definition: of an approach to a problem that begins at the highest conceptual level and works down to the details
Example: a top-down analysis might begin by looking at macro-economic trends; top-down programming
Synonyms: BOTTOM-UP, of, an, approach, to, a, problem, that, begins, at, the, highest, conceptual, level, and, works, down, details, top-down, analysis, might, begin, by, looking, macro-economic, trends, programming
Category: adj.all
